question1: How do I book a vehicle through your website?
answer1: To book a vehicle, simply choose the type of service you need, select the date and time, enter the value of the product, specify any additional labour required, and provide the pickup and delivery locations. Once you filled out the necessary information, submit your booking request to receive quotes from our partners.
question2: How long does it take to receive a quote after booking?
answer2: Once the booking request is submitted, our module will obtain quotes from partners within 5 seconds. You'll receive the top 3 lowest price to choose from.
question3: Can I choose my preferred vendor?
answer3: Yes! After receiving quotes, you can select the vendor that best fits your budget and requirements.
question4: What payment options do you offer?
answer4: You can choose to pay the full amount upfront or pay a partial advance. Payment methods include credit/debit card and other secure options available on our site.
question5: How can I track my order?
answer5: After your booking is confirmed and the order has started, you can view the live location of your vehicle in the 'Booking' section. You'll receive detailed information including the vendor name, operator name, the type of vehicle selected, as well as the booking status and payment status for your convenience.
question6: Will I be notified when my driver is arriving?
answer6: Yes, the driver will notify you once they are en route to your location, ensuring you are informed about their arrival time.
question7: What should I do if I need to cancel my booking?
answer7: If you need to cancel your booking, you can easily do so by clicking the cancel icon located in the top right corner during the vendor selection process. Follow the prompts to complete your cancellation.
question8: Are there any additional fees that I should be aware of?
answer8: While we aim to provide clear pricing, additional fees may apply based on specific services or circumstances. This will be disclosed in the quotes you receive.
question9: What happens if my vehicle does not arrive on time?
answer9: If your vehicle is late, please contact our support team. We will assist you in tracking the status and addressing the issues.
question10: How do I contact customer support?
answer10: You can reach our customer support team via the report section on the website or email us. We are here to assist you 24 hours a day.

partnerQuestion2: What are the sizes and type of truck?
partnerAnswer2: We provide a shipping platform of multiple sizes, Which are as follows: trailer, truck, lorry, diana, and pickup truck.
partnerAnswer3: We have our own trucks and we also have contracts with transportation agents throughout the kingdom.
partnerQuestion4: I have a furniture that I need to move. What shipping platform can you provide me with and what are the condition?
partnerAnswer4: To reserve a truck for transporting furniture, you can request the truck through the application, and to find out the prices through the application, specify the loading and delivery address and it will appear for your price automatically 1.Loading and unloading workers can be requested for an additional fee through the application 2.Furniture should be well wrapped to prevent damage 3.We do not provide shipping packaging or dismantling and installation services 4.In shipping, we provide rental trucks to transport all type of products, and we do not specialize in transporting furniture in particular
partnerQuestion5: We have a load of 30 tons and we need a trailer to transport it. is that possible?
partnerAnswer5: The maximum load that can be loaded in 25 tons and it is not possible to load more than that, but there are exceptional cases in which we provide assistance to our customers continuing to move higher than that if necessary.
partnerQuestion6: What products are prohibited from being transported on a shipping platform?
partnerAnswer6: The transportation of all products prohibited by the kingdom of Saudi Arabia is prohibited. it is also prohibits the transportation of people, flammable materials, and the transportation of money.

partnerQuestion8: What is the maximum weight that can be loaded per truck?

partnerQuestion9: How many pallets can be loaded per truck?

partnerQuestion10: Can a driver of a specific nationality be provided?
partnerAnswer10: Drivers of specific nationalities can be provided according to the customer's request for reason of entering government facilities or according to followed regulations and policies of some companies.
partnerQuestion11: What are the nationalities of your driver?
partnerAnswer11: We have all nationalities of drivers working with us, Saudis and non-Saudis
partnerQuestion12: Can you provide us with a fixed price that is not based on kilometers
partnerAnswer12: The policy of the shipping platform requires that the price be calculated according to the estimated distance between the loading point and the delivery point, so you may find that prices vary depending on this distance.
